# ğŸ“¢ TTS Caller (Clojure + MaryTTS + Baresip)

A lightweight voice alert service that converts text to speech (TTS) and initiates SIP phone calls.  
Built with **Clojure**, using **MaryTTS** for speech synthesis and **Baresip** for SIP call handling.

Perfect for integration with monitoring systems like **Zabbix**, **ElastAlert**, **Alertmanager**, **Centreon**, and others.

